WEBVTT

1
01:09:45.590 --> 01:09:47.310 
来了一个大浪。
Here comes the big one.

2
01:09:47.350 --> 01:09:49.880 
啊！快点！你别错过机会！
Ooh! Come on! You gotta try this!

3
01:09:49.920 --> 01:09:53.190 
-你能不能别闹了？ -为什么？有什么问题吗？
- Will you just stop it? - Why? What's wrong?

4
01:09:53.230 --> 01:09:55.520 
我们在鲸鱼的肚子里面， 你还不明白吗？
We're in a whale, don't you get it?

5
01:09:55.560 --> 01:09:56.720 
-鲸鱼？ -一头鲸鱼！
- Whale? - A whale!

6
01:09:56.760 --> 01:09:59.490 
这都怪你问什么路！ 这就是问路的下场！
You had to ask for help! And now we're stuck here!

7
01:09:59.530 --> 01:10:02.300 
鲸鱼。你知道的， 我懂鲸语。
Wow, a whale. I speak whale.

8
01:10:02.340 --> 01:10:04.670 
不，你疯了！你根本不会说鲸语！
No, you're insane! You can't speak whale!

9
01:10:04.700 --> 01:10:07.900 
我得出去！我得去找我儿子！
I have to get out! I have to find my son!

10
01:10:07.940 --> 01:10:13.350 
我的告诉他海龟有多老！
I have to tell him how old sea turtles are!

